title: When people BM because they won a 5v3
body:
Smh

It's like they completely forgot I went 7/0 against them in lane.
Just because you got fed by 5v1'ing the poor Caitlyn 2 billion times doesn't actually make you good.. It's not like I can be everywhere at once. And even if all of us could, what's 3 people going to do against Naut, Ali, and 3 mobile damage dealers?
